extends ../main-layout

block headAppendTitle
    title TJ Tech - Customer Support

block content
    .container.pt-5.crm-service
        .row
            .col-12.col-xl-3
                .text-intro.text-nowrap.mt-5 We Build Trust
                .text-intro-explain.text-mt.text-nowrap With All Our Fintech Solutions
                .button-mb-center
                    a(href="contact.html")
                        button.btn-base.learn-btn Learn More
            .col-12.col-xl-9
                img(style='width: 100%;' src='assets/images/p_ecosystem.svg' alt='')
        .g-header.text-center.head-spacing Customer Support
        .row.leading
            .coml-first-img
                    img(src="assets/images/customer-support.png", alt="")
            .figure.col-12.col-lg-5.coml-none
                .image-shadow
                img.main-image(src='assets/images/customer-support.png' alt='')
            .descriptor.col-12.col-lg-7
                .descriptor-item.d-flex.align-items-start
                    img(src='assets/images/ic_mini_rounded_tick.svg' alt='')
                    .detail The customer support function is responsible for handling queries from users through email. For example, if a customer makes a deposit which is delayed (normally resulting in a complaint through email) the operational team will be responsible for tracing the transaction, justifying the account balance and responding to the customer.
                .descriptor-item.d-flex.align-items-start.mt-4
                    img(src='assets/images/ic_mini_rounded_tick.svg' alt='')
                    .detail TJ Tech prides itself not only on the quality of our products but also on the exceptional level of customer support it provides. Their 24/7 customer support is available to assist with any questions or concern. Technology can sometimes be challenging, and a dedicated team of support agents is available to help ensure products and services are seamless and stress-free.
